snippet.title: Super Club Soccer Trailer - FREE MULTIPLAYER SOCCER GAME ON STEAM
snippet.description:
Get Super Club Soccer here for FREE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/744980/Super_Club_Soccer/
Visit Our Website:
https://www.superclubsoccer.com/

Super Club Soccer is a turn based online soccer game. Teams take turns making their moves in an intense tactical battle. Each player is controlled by an individual user so communication is key. Create your player and train them up while you find a club and progress in the tournament system. Follow the tutorial when you first open the game to get a grip of the game mechanics, from there you can go into quick play matches to hone your skills. Once you're in a team check the schedule to find out when your next match is and let your manager know your availability in the match lobby screen.

Create your soccer story.
